        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You might not remember your past, but some part of you has an innate understanding of the basic layout and user interfaces of ancient pre-Gap technology. You become trained in your choice of Computers or Crafting. If you're already trained in both, you instead become trained in a Lore skill related to technology. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Recall Knowledge] checks using Computers, Crafting, or Piloting to identify ancient technology designed before the Gap.</p>"
